SELECT <%=sourceSystem%>  || 'ProductionOrderItem_' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || '_' || "AFPO"."AUFNR" || '_' || "AFPO"."POSNR" AS "ID",
       CAST("AFPO"."ETRMP" AS TIMESTAMP)                                                                                AS "CreationTime",
       "AFPO"."PSMNG"                                                                                                   AS "OrderItemQuantity",
       "AFPO"."MEINS"                                                                                                   AS "BaseQuantityUnit",
       "AFPO"."WEMNG"                                                                                                   AS "GoodsReceiptQuantity",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || 'ProductionOrder_' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || '_' || "AFPO"."AUFNR"                                    AS "Header",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || 'Plant_' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || "AFPO"."DWERK"                                                     AS "Plant",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || 'MaterialMasterPlant_' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || "AFPO"."MATNR"
       || "AFPO"."DWERK"                                                                                                AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
       'SAP'                                                                                                            AS "SourceSystemType",
       "AFPO"."MANDT"                                                                                                   AS "SourceSystemInstance",
       CAST("AFPO"."AUFNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                             AS "SystemProductionOrderNumber",
       CAST("AFPO"."POSNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                             AS "SystemProductionOrderItemNumber",
       CAST("AFPO"."AUFNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                             AS "DatabaseProductionOrderNumber",
       CAST("AFPO"."POSNR" AS VARCHAR(255))                                                                             AS "DatabaseProductionOrderItemNumber",
       "AFPO"."XLOEK"                                                                                                   AS "DeletionFlag",
       "AFPO"."ELIKZ"                                                                                                   AS "DeliveryCompletedIndicator",
	<%=sourceSystem%>  || 'Material_' || "AFPO"."MANDT" || "AFPO"."MATNR"                                                  AS "Material"
FROM "AFPO" AS "AFPO"
         LEFT JOIN "AUFK" AS "AUFK"
                   ON "AFPO"."MANDT" = "AUFK"."MANDT"
                       AND "AFPO"."AUFNR" = "AUFK"."AUFNR"
WHERE "AFPO"."MANDT" IS NOT NULL
  AND "AUFK"."AUTYP" IN ('10')
